3. exd5 { Take back the pawn! } 3... cxd5 4. Nf3 { Get your knight out to attack the pawn! } 4... Nc6 5. Be2 { Get the other knight out! } 5... Nf6 6. O-O { Get the bishop out! } 6... Bg4 7. Nc3 { Close the center up with your pawn } 7... e6 { [%csl Gd6][%cal Gf8d6] } *


